def: A kind of sugar confection which dissolves easily in the mouth.Thackeray.
An undergraduate, partly supported by the college funds, whoseduty it formerly was to wait at table. A servitor corresponded to asizar in Cambridge and Dublin universities.
Of or pertaining to histolysis, or the degeneration of tissues.
The stingfish, or lesser weever (Tranchinus vipera).
A tribe of Indians of the Dakota stock, living in Montana; --also called Upsarokas.
Making red; as, rubific rays. Grew.
Pertaining to the time before the Passover, or before Easter.
